{
  "stem": "7094.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was good and bad, in a way, because she-- maybe she meant it well, but she was very tactless.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, she still hasn't outgrown-- she brought with her not the good quality, but the bad quality for the small shtetl.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She inherited not the good qualities of the eastern, but the bad qualities of-- and the mixture was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- I needed a different treatment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, she would-- wanted to know what happened to the family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So if I told her, she said, yes, if somebody of my family would have survived-- and there was I, so clinging, wanting the family.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But to her, you know, I was so far removed that I wasn't family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then she would say-- not thinking about it, not because she was a bad woman, she was just tactless.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She would say, yes, good people didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It means, 'the rubbish survived.' But this is the reaction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So very soon after that, I shut up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I realized.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is how it is in life, somehow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Something you do, and you get it back in one form or another.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was on the boat, because I was one of the oldest one, I wanted to help Rabbi Schonfeld.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could see-- I have photographs where there were children of three and older.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was the one who emptied the sick bags, because we didn't have any nurses around, and who looked after the smaller children.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were very lucky, because we got crates of fruit, which was a rarity.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, in Poland, even before the war, the only time you had an orange, when you were dying.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there we had, for the first time, some apples, some fruit.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
